rating_comment: Staying at Michelle place was a pleasent. Room was big, clean and fresh. Michelle is very helpfull and nice host. I would recommend this place to everyone who is on the way to Sikkim or on the way back. Close to the airport, surrounded with nature.
Great place to stay
an amazing place with beautiful interiors with clean furnishings. Host was very responsive and it will be our go to home whenever we visit Bagdogra.
Gr8 Place and Value for Money

I stayed with many kind and helpful hosts while in West Bengal, but Michelle stands out. She is a great host, her rooms are clean, the location is quiet and her knowledge of the surrounding areas useful. Thank you for two great stays, Michelle!
Michelle has been a most kind and helpful host. The room was new and very clean. The area was wonderfully quiet and I slept well. I will be staying again at Michelle’s place on my return journey.
Michelle’s place was the perfect spot to stay for one night on our way up to Darjeeling. She is a wonderful host and has thought of everything you might need to be comfortable.
Stayed ine night to go airport, excellent.
Loved the room! The stay was very comfortable

Wow what a beautiful place. Spotlessly clean, really nice touches that give the room a comfortable and welcoming feel. We were delayed in reaching Michelle and exhausted by the time we arrived. Michelle was considerate and understanding and couldn’t be more helpful. We had a good night sleep before setting off, sad that we couldn’t spend more time with this lovely family. Great breakfast, thank you so much for everything and regards to your kind Papa

Amazing home stay . Michelle is really smart and replies to all the queries and doubts in a timely manner . We were new to the place and struggled to catch up the language , she would talk to taxi/rikshaw drivers and always made sure our journey is safe .Would totally like to book again soon .
Everything was great about the airbnb. Michelle was really helpful. The rooms were clean and cosy. Enjoyed staying here.
The place was peaceful, clean and comfort at its best. And Michelle is a very responsive and helpful host. Highly recommended.
Mitchelle was very helpful…good place about 10-15 minutes drive to Bagdogra Airport…she arranged packed Indian food for us early morning and a cab to airport…
The stay was really good. The food provided was tasty and homemade .more importantly the host behavior was great

Very clean beautiful place, friendly
Arranged vehicle for me to air port
Will visit again
Really loved Michelle's place and everything was on point.
Michelle's place was clean, extra pillows were provided, lunch was scrambled out as we were hungry. Very satisfactory stay.

Michelle is extremely responsive. Her family makes you feel at home.
Her friend is also very helpful. He will help you with all the necessary recommendations.
Only disappointment was the food. It's definately not worth the price.
I would definately stay at Michelle's place again and give a hard pass to food.
Very Friendly and Responsive Host. They were flexible in timings. Good Home made food

I stayed overnight, it was a very comfortable and secure stay. Michelle always responded promptly. Had a homely dinner and Breakfast. The host also helped me with arranging an auto for dropping me at the airport. I will book this place again if staying at Bagdogra.
A nice host, felt like home. happy and friendly faces.

Good place, well maintained. Host was very helpful and available in case of any issues.
Good hospitality, they have a very beautiful garden inside a compound which added a charm. Breakfast could have been better but overall totally worth the price paid.

As always, the listing was perfect. I booked a different unit this time and it was more suitable more me. The amenities were top notch. The host and her family treats me like a family member and this makes the entire experience very fulfilling.
Great Host and great listing.
